&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for an enthusiastic Transformation and Innovation Lead to join the Tier 4 CAMHS bed based provision in delivering services to the young people of Cheshire and Merseyside. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post holder will assist agencies and professionals to implement the Tier 4 CASHS model of care through collaborative and innovation approaches. Responsible for service improvement through monitoring and evaluating themes that arise from service user and stakeholders engagement to influence integrated service delivery.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Joy Fenna Head of Service - CAMHS Email address joy.fenna@nhs.net Telephone number 01244 397269&lt;/p&gt;
